{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were told to stick to our luggage because we will need it, and make sure you've got your warm things ready, and all sorts of rather comforting, reassuring talk, all designed to keep us less nervous, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at one point, the very German soldier that I asked to please help me, that I had no luggage at all, actually offered to take me home to the ghetto, where we had not been for a long, long time, so that we could gather some clothing.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not much older than I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he was about 17, in uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember him asking me, 'You're not Jewish, are you?' And I thought, oh, here is an out, the first time it happened to me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course I realized once I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pointed out my sister, there was no possibility of carrying that through.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I did tell him I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no mistake about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, 'Never mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll take you home.' And Vera had to stay back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her ankle was very swollen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he took me back to the ghetto, where I hadn't been for quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was terrified of walking in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The evidence of my mother's departure was clear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The flat hadn't been ransacked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The beds were like beds that people sort of in a hurry left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was an extremely, extremely difficult moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was trying-- he told me that he had very little time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was trying to gather a suitcase full of stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And suddenly, I found I was alone in the room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know where he had disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was standing over me all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
